<p>Do you not have 6-10 hours to dedicate on a weekend or evening to play in Magic: The Gathering tournaments? Tournament rounds held on this site are run over seven <em>days</em> to provide a more casual atmosphere. It allows busy people who don't have the time to block out an entire day of their weekend or blow their whole evening to participate in both free tournaments and paid, prize supported tournaments.</p>
